{"tid":1826941,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"適逢2020年是庚子年，中方向美方加購2000億美元貨品，史稱\"庚子賠款\"","createTime":"2020-01-16T14:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T14:45:31.000Z","uid":30788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6012d40cf092116ec39ce1e985c24b4cd09d6104","tid":1826941,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"庚子賠款總額為關二千億美元，約合當時的一萬四千億美元或1500億英鎊或22萬億日元或12.3萬億盧布。賠款年息為15厘關稅（15%），分兩年還清。<br />\n<br />\n庚子賠款，又稱庚子事變賠款、中美貿易賠款，簡稱庚款，是中共政府在2019年5月與美國簽訂的《第一階段協議》中所規定的賠款，因系針對2020年（庚子年）小粉紅發起的庚子事變，引致八國聯軍出兵中國，因此被稱為庚子賠款。"},{"pid":"b8ce850787c21ce6dd839facbe1470f9f4994691","tid":1826941,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:06:30.000Z","msg":"中共簽得呢次<br />\n其他國家有樣學樣加支那關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一齊簽協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0af3b7234ea26694333e9af60fc5fb728fa68df","tid":1826941,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c0e9b9c0c836afa7cb78bca281acfe343a6fe7","tid":1826941,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"傳去支那"},{"pid":"82ea465ca7d28d2b875e40efb9ba7ef030b7107d","tid":1826941,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}